                    line-height: 1.5;">
                    <i>Nightcrawler</i> is not an average crime-thriller movie from Dan Gilroy, who co-wrote “The Bourne Legacy.” Jake Gyllenhaal as Lou Bloom plays a cameraman who explores the dark and mysterious world of L.A.’s crime journalism, scratching the underbelly of the Los Angeles underworld.</p>
